"A 'move line like' model, ie having at least debit, credit, date, account_id"
" and company_id fields. This model is the data source for column Actuals."
msgstr ""
"Model, podoben postavkam knjiženja, tj. ima vsaj polja debit, credit, date, "
"account_id in company_id. Ta model je vir podatkov za stolpec Dejanski."

